These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, colombian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, goldfish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the australian##1
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the malaysian is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
7. the indonesian is somewhere between the australian and the owner of the horse##7
8. the indonesian and the owner of the frog have the same parity positions##9
9. the colombian and the owner of the chinchilla have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | australian | indonesian | colombian     | malaysian |
| Pet           | goldfish   | frog     | horse | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, reading, cooking, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
7. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate    | lemonade | milk    |
| Hobby      | board-games | reading | cooking      | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, hot-chocolate, water
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, pomegranate, kiwi, corn
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
2. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
8. the person drinking juice and the person eating pomegranate have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | juice    | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea    | water  |
| Food       | pomegranate | corn | cabbage | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, fisherman, bartender
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, metal, salsa
1. the fan disco is the entrepreneur##1
2. the fan country is on the right of the fan metal##1
3. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
4. the fan salsa is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
5. the fan country is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the bartender and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
7. the fisherman is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | bartender | fisherman | doctor  | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | metal             | country          | salsa | disco    |

