2. the owner of the lizard and the fan house have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the horse and the fan d&b have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan r&b##1
6. the fan d&b is not the owner of the horse##6
7. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan house##1
9. the owner of the goldfish is not the fan r&b##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | house | reggae | r&b  | d&b |
| Pet           | horse   | lizard     | frog | goldfish      |

