.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, romance, western
There are 4 different nationalities: german, british, malaysian, canadian
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the german and the person watching romance movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching western movies and the german have different parity positions##9
6. the malaysian is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
7. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the canadian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel | romance | western |
| Nationality   | canadian        | malaysian    | german   | british |

