4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the fan blues is not to the right of the fan techno##8
6. the fan jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5
7. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | jazz | blues         | techno     |
| Sport         | cycling | ice-hockey  | water-polo | rugby |

