3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
7. the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
