.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry, pumpkin, cauliflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, ship, bike
1. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
2. the person eating cauliflower and the person driving the bike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the bike##7
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pumpkin | raspberry   | strawberry | cauliflower |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | scooter    | bike      |

