The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, baking, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating lime have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | eggplant | plum | peach   | lime   |
| Hobby   | card-games  | baking   | traveling | drawing |

