.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, techno, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, van, quad-bike, tram
1. the fan pop is on the right of the fan techno##1
2. the fan techno is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the fan dubstep and the person driving the van have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the tram is the fan dubstep##1
5. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | dubstep  | techno | pop    |
| Transport     | quad-bike | tram | train  | van |

