.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, grapefruit, grapes, eggplant
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, chinese, german, thai
1. the person eating eggplant is not the thai##6
2. the thai is not to the right of the russian##8
3. the person eating grapes is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the german##3
6. the thai is on the far left##1
7. the russian is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
8. the person eating lettuce is the chinese##1
9. the person eating eggplant and the russian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit   | eggplant    | grapes | lettuce    |
| Nationality   | thai | russian | german   | chinese |

