The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, trance, ambient
1. the person eating grapes and the fan ambient have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan ambient is not to the left of the person eating grapes##8
3. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the fan dubstep and the fan ambient##7
4. the fan ambient is somewhere between the fan trance and the person eating pomegranate##7
5. the fan pop is not the person eating cauliflower##6
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person eating corn is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | cauliflower | pomegranate | grapes | corn  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | pop | ambient | trance |

