.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, milk, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, horror, time-travel
1. the person watching western movies is not the person drinking juice##6
2. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person watching western movies and the person drinking iced-tea have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching horror movies and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | coffee  | milk  | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | horror | time-travel | western      |

