.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, classical, ambient, gospel
 1. the person drinking cola and the fan ambient have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 3. the fan d&b is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking fanta##7
 4. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan ambient is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person drinking water and the fan classical have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan gospel##3
 9. the fan gospel is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking water is not to the right of the fan d&b##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | water | soy-milk  | cola |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | ambient     | d&b | classical     |

