3. the nurse is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
4. the journalist is not to the right of the teacher##8
5. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the pony and the entrepreneur have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the frog and the nurse have the same parity positions##9

