The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, sudoku, chess, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is cooking have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | iced-tea | coffee | fanta |
| Hobby      | chess | cooking   | sudoku   | singing   |

