.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, 7up, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, card-games, collecting
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is cooking have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 9. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is cooking have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | 7up        | sprite   | tea      |
| Hobby      | collecting | card-games | cooking | chess |

 